dc_description_s: This data layer represents roads for Dane County, Wisconsin in 2011. [This layer is a detailed line coverage of the Dane County roadway network containing attributes such as street name and address ranges, and features including public and named private roadways.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://gis-countyofdane.opendata.arcgis.com/.
